A vintage 1960s educational filmstrip aesthetic showing a gleaming desktop computer monitor displaying a glowing fish swimming through digital waves, the fish rendered in warm amber and sepia tones with subtle scan lines across the image, set against a classroom backdrop with an old wooden desk and chalkboard shadows, the composition evoking mid-century optimism about technology and learning, soft grain texture throughout, muted yellows and browns with pops of teal from the digital elements emerging from the screen.
